1600:I couldn't calm down in the slightest.\p;
1700:Not just because of the earthquake...\n;And not because of the headache, either...\p;
1800:It wasn't just those... but a certain urge that was threatening to overtake me.\p;
1900:For some reason, walking around like this... It made me feel like...\p;
2000:I wanted to kill someone.\p;
2100:By the time I got to the school gate, the anxiety and sense of dread I'd been feeling were increasing by the second.\p;
2200:I had the chills.\n;My body wouldn't stop shivering.\n;And my headache was coming back.\p;
2300:When I looked closely, I noticed a group of students formed around the third year building.\p;
2400:I looked for Rimi within them.\p;
2500:For some odd reason, everyone was looking toward the top of the building, and even those who weren't soon followed suit—almost like a bunch of lemmings.\p;
2600:〔Misumi〕“Oh, Taku!”\p;
2700:Misumi-kun rushed over to me.\p;
2800:I should ask him where Rimi was...\p;
2900:〔Misumi〕“Look who decided to come to school today!”\p;
3000:〔Misumi〕“Actually, I'll save the pissin' you off for later...”\p;
3100:He looked gravely serious, and his face was pale.\n;Seeing Misumi-kun like this was very unusual.\p;
3200:What the hell was going on?\p;
3300:〔Misumi〕“Things are bad right now, man... Real bad...”\p;
3400:“Things are bad?”\n;What did that mean? What was bad?\p;
